    AbortMultiUploadRequest, AppendObjectRequest, CompleteMultiUploadRequest, DeleteBucketCORSRequest, DeleteBucketLifecycleRequest, DeleteBucketRequest, DeleteBucketTaggingRequest, DeleteMultiObjectRequest, DeleteObjectRequest, GetBucketACLRequest, GetBucketCORSRequest, GetBucketLifecycleRequest, GetBucketLocationRequest, GetBucketRequest, GetBucketTaggingRequest, GetObjectACLRequest, GetObjectRequest, GetServiceRequest, HeadBucketRequest, HeadObjectRequest, InitMultipartUploadRequest, ListMultiUploadsRequest, ListPartsRequest, OptionObjectRequest, PutBucketACLRequest, PutBucketCORSRequest, PutBucketLifecycleRequest, PutBucketRequest, PutBucketTaggingRequest, PutObjectACLRequest, PutObjectRequest, UploadPartRequest

    public abstract class CosXmlRequest
extends QCloudHttpRequest

    COS XML服务请求的基类，主要包含了请求的公共参数和 公共HTTP头部文档 设置。

    其中需要您关心的公共请求头部有：

    • Authorization : setSign(long, Set, Set)，必须设置
    • Content-MD5 : setContentMd5(String)，可选设置，默认为空
    • Expect : setExpect(String) ，可选设置，默认为空
